EXTRACTED VALUE: Marcus Camby bounced back after a miserable game on Friday, scoring 12 points and grabbing 19 rebounds in a fiesty win against the visiting Clippers.
Emeka Okafor hit 12-of-13 shots for a season high 26 points, 13 rebounds and a block against Joel Anthony, Chris Bosh and the Heat on Friday.
Tyler Hansbrough played just seven minutes on Monday, finishing with four points on 2-of-2 shooting with no other statistics.
D.J. Augustin played through a sinus infection on Wednesday and had 13 points, six assists and a 3-pointer in the loss.
